metadata.name: It's The Climb
metadata.description:
In life no matter where we are going , whatever the destination maybe , it's the journey that matters the most like on a hike reaching the hill top is the destination but the moments we experience on the climb that we remember.

The climb is a photo that shows how the scale of us humans is so small compared to the climb that we all are on in our lives , so we need to enjoy the climb as it is because these are the moments we will remember the most when the destination is reached.
